        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 2,
      "content": "The other bunnies pick sweet berries in the field. Then, little Peter runs quickly off and out of sight.",
      "source_page_number": 2,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_002.jpg",
        "filename": "page_002.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
