        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 5,
      "content": "Suddenly, Mr. McGregor saw Peter playing in the sunny garden. He quickly started running with his big rake after poor little Peter.",
      "source_page_number": 5,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_005.jpg",
        "filename": "page_005.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_3/page_005.mp3",
        "filename": "page_005.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 6,
      "content": "Because of the chase, Peter quickly found a spot to hide from danger. He tucked himself inside the cool watering can for safety.",
      "source_page_number": 6,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_006.jpg",
        "filename": "page_006.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_3/page_006.mp3",
        "filename": "page_006.mp3",
        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 7,
      "content": "Next, he runs toward the gate, but he loses his blue jacket somewhere. He needs to get home before it is too late.",
      "source_page_number": 7,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_007.jpg",
        "filename": "page_007.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_3/page_007.mp3",
