        "content_type": "audio/mpeg",
        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 8,
      "content": "Finally, Peter gets home safely at night, though he feels very unwell. He rests in his bed and sleeps for a long time.",
      "source_page_number": 8,
